This file contains abbreviated installation instructions for FEATURE 3.1.0. For
more installation details, see the FEATURE 3.1.0 User Manual, available as part
of this release and in the downloads page at the FEATURE website on SimTK
(http://simtk.org/home/feature).

Note that FEATURE 3.1.0 depends on GNU GCC, GNU make, and zlib; make sure your
system has these software packages prior to proceeding to install FEATURE

To build FEATURE from the command-line, change directories to the location of
the FEATURE 3.1.0 source release download tar file and type the following
instructions:

$ tar -xvzf feature-3.1.0-src.tar.gz
$ cd feature-3.1.0
$ make
$ sudo make install
